    <p class="pg-sub">Finding vegan candy used to mean squinting at ingredient lists and Googling "is gelatin vegan?" at the grocery store. Not anymore. We tested over 50 vegan candy brands across every category — gummy bears, sour gummies, chocolate, fruit snacks, lollipops, and hard candy — to identify the 15 best that taste as good as (or better than) their non-vegan counterparts.</p>
