    <p>Gummy bears are where vegans face the biggest challenge — traditional gummy bears are defined by gelatin, the animal-derived protein that creates their iconic bounce. Pectin-based alternatives have improved dramatically, and these four brands prove that vegan gummy bears can rival gelatin originals. For an in-depth comparison of all <a href="/candy/gelatin-free-gummy-candy/">gelatin-free gummy candy</a> options, see our dedicated guide.</p>

    <!-- PRODUCT 1 — SURF SWEETS -->
