    <p>Surf Sweets earns the #1 spot because they eliminate every possible vegan concern: organic sugar (no bone char), pectin gelling (no gelatin), real fruit juice colors (no animal-tested dyes), and third-party vegan certification. The texture is genuinely impressive — a soft, satisfying chew that rivals Haribo in blind taste tests. This is the vegan gummy we hand to skeptics to prove that plant-based candy has arrived.</p>

