    <p>SmartSweets proves that vegan candy can also be healthy candy. At 3g sugar per bag, these pectin-fiber gummy bears let health-conscious vegans enjoy candy without the glycemic impact. The allulose-based sweetener system avoids the bone-char sugar question entirely, and the 28g of soluble corn fiber per bag feeds beneficial gut bacteria. For a deeper look at pectin formulation, see our <a href="/candy/pectin-gummy-candy/">pectin gummy candy</a> guide.</p>

